---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="AI Search Ecosystem Services | Rank4AI" description="AI search visibility built outside your website. Google ecosystem from £800/mo. Core ecosystem £1,300/mo. Full ecosystem £2,500/mo. No code changes, no disruption.">

<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-tag">Ecosystem Services – No Site Work</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Ecosystem Services</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Everything we build sits outside your existing website. We do not touch your site, your code or your current setup.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">Rather than waiting for AI platforms to find your business, we place content and signals directly into the infrastructure those platforms already trust.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-xl text-teal mb-2">Google Foundation</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-4">£800<span class="text-sm text-text-muted font-body"> / month</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">The starting point. Your business established across Google's own platforms and visible to Google Search, AI Overviews and Gemini.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-text-muted space-y-2">
          <li>AI Visibility Audit</li>
          <li>Core presence across Google platforms</li>
          <li>External directory alignment</li>
          <li>Site asset pack for your team</li>
          <li>Monthly action document</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card border-teal">
        <h3 class="!text-xl text-teal mb-2">Core Ecosystem</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-4">£1,300<span class="text-sm text-text-muted font-body"> / month</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">Everything in Google, plus Microsoft/Bing, LinkedIn, wider web. All six AI platforms covered directly.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-text-muted space-y-2">
          <li>Everything in Google Foundation</li>
          <li>Microsoft and Bing ecosystem</li>
          <li>Wider web: directories, reviews, citations</li>
          <li>All six AI platforms addressed directly</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-xl text-teal mb-2">Full Ecosystem</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-4">£2,500<span class="text-sm text-text-muted font-body"> / month</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">Complete coverage. Every signal layer built and maintained simultaneously across Google, Microsoft/Bing, and the wider web.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-text-muted space-y-2">
          <li>Everything in Core Ecosystem</li>
          <li>Share of Voice PR strategy</li>
          <li>Data authority assets</li>
          <li>Developer community presence</li>
          <li>120-200+ active touchpoints</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="mb-4">Add-Ons</h2>
      <div class="card-teal-border mb-4">
        <h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Microsoft and Bing</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Available as a standalone add-on to any Google tier. Expands coverage into ChatGPT and Copilot directly via Bing, LinkedIn and Microsoft's own platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-teal-border mb-10">
        <h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Advisory</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Research, audit and planning delivered as standalone deliverables. Suitable for businesses with internal teams who can execute. Priced per deliverable.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="mb-4">What Builds Over Time</h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">As signals become more consistent across more trusted sources, AI systems develop greater confidence in your business. That confidence is what produces inclusion in AI-generated answers.</p>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">It compounds over time. The businesses that build it now, while most competitors are not thinking about it, will be very difficult to displace once that confidence is established.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-24 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Get Started</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted mb-10 max-w-[500px] mx-auto">Every engagement begins with the AI Search Visibility Audit.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
